    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Completed和Failed是Retry或Reset回Idle，但Cancelled也是Reset。还有，Completed要通知Etcd集群，Cancelled要通知Worker节点，这是关键的外部系统交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
